vidma - Virtual Disks Manipulator
=================================

Utility for manipulating virtual disk images.


Supported operations
--------------------

* resize


Supported formats
-----------------

* fixed-size VDI (Virtual Disk Image), used by VirtualBox


Requirements
------------

* little-endian machine (e.g. x86, x86-64)
* POSIX OS (e.g. Linux) or Windows


CAUTION!
--------

Program is in ALPHA stage, therefore it's considered HARMFUL and UNSAFE!
You have been warned! USE AT YOUR OWN RISK! NO WARRANTY!
